List of the type trunk_vlans. Specify VLANs, or ranges thereof, that the interface may carry when in trunk mode. If not specified, all VLANs are allowed on the interface. Ranges are specified in the form x..y, where x<y - ranges are assumed to be inclusive (such that the VLAN range is x <= range <= y.
